data.description: Make this Ranch in Livonia your Home! This Home Offers Three Bedrooms, One Bath, Nice Size Living Room, Full Basement Partially Finished, Shed,Two Car Garage with a newer roof.  Nice Size Eat in Kitchen with Wood Floors and all the Appliances Stay, Property is completely Fenced with Gated access to Elm Park.  New Furnace (3 yrs) and Hot Water Heater.  Double Pane Vinyl Windows, Ungraded Electrical Panel with a Hook up for a Generator.
